title: Doom bots Icon
body: I won a game of Doom boots and still dont have the icon.

replies.body: i read that it must be added till nov 3 and if not i should contact riot support

As *Zombiemaster* mentioned, we're still granting all of the Teemoing Icons until **November 17th**, so if you don't have it by then, I'd definitely encourage you to reach out in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new).

Let me know if you have any questions.

http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/game-updates/special-event/it-will-all-be-over-soon

> Icons should appear in your account up to two weeks after November 3, 2016 at 23:59 PT, so fret not, dear followers. I am a dark yordle of my word.
The icons can take up to 2 weeks after November 3rd to be added to your account.
